# Digital Companion — Project Rules

Rules guide. Skills do. Commands trigger. (CO_PM_RESEARCH)

## Commands

- `./gradlew assembleDebug` — Build debug APK
- `./gradlew test` — Run unit tests
- `./gradlew installDebug` — Install on device/emulator
- `./gradlew :app:lintDebug` — Lint check

## Code Style

- Kotlin strict, Jetpack Compose
- SDK via facade: no CxrApi in UI; use RokidSdkFacade
- See `app/src/main/java/.../MainActivity.kt` for canonical Compose pattern

## Workflow

- Plan Mode (Shift+Tab) vóór grote wijzigingen
- Reference files: `@ARCHITECTURE.md`, `@rokidsdk.md`
